"title": "5830: delight",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5830: delight",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A sense of joy and pleasure, experienced especially through achievements or relationships.</p>\n<h2>God as the source of delight</h2>\n<h3>Delight in the person of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:10\">ISA 61:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh1:11\">NEH 1:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job22:26\">JOB 22:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:8\">PSA 22:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:4\">PSA 37:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps43:3-Ps43:4\">PSA 43:3–43:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa58:13-Isa58:14\">ISA 58:13–58:14</a></p>\n<h3>Delight in the word of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:16\">PSA 119:16</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:22\">ROM 7:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps1:2\">PSA 1:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:7-Ps19:14\">PSA 19:7–19:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:24\">PSA 119:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:47\">PSA 119:47</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer15:16\">JER 15:16</a></p>\n<h3>Delight in the works of God</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:1\">1SA 2:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps35:4-Ps35:10\">PSA 35:4–35:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:23\">ACT 11:23</a></p>\n<h2>God expresses delight</h2>\n<h3>Over his world</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:31\">PSA 104:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:31\">GEN 1:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:30-Prov8:31\">PRO 8:30–8:31</a></p>\n<h3>Over his people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut30:9-Deut30:10\">DEU 30:9–30:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:20\">2SA 22:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:10-Ps147:11\">PSA 147:10–147:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps149:4\">PSA 149:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa62:4\">ISA 62:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:18-Isa65:19\">ISA 65:18–65:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:20\">JER 31:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:41\">JER 32:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic7:18\">MIC 7:18</a></p>\n<h3>Over justice</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:1\">PRO 11:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:20\">PRO 11:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:22\">PRO 12:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:24\">JER 9:24</a></p>\n<h3>Over his Messiah</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt3:17\">MAT 3:17</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:11\">MRK 1:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:22\">LUK 3:22</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:1\">ISA 42:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:18-Matt12:21\">MAT 12:18–12:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:5\">MAT 17:5</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:7\">MRK 9:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:35\">LUK 9:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:17\">2PE 1:17</a></p>\n<h3>God's delight is absent when something is viewed unfavourably</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam15:22\">1SA 15:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:31\">LEV 26:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:16\">PSA 51:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:10\">PSA 147:10</a></p>\n<h2>Natural delight in parenthood</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:12\">PRO 3:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:24\">PRO 23:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:17\">PRO 29:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic1:16\">MIC 1:16</a></p>\n<h2>Sexual delight</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song1:4\">SNG 1:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen34:19\">GEN 34:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov5:18\">PRO 5:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song2:3\">SNG 2:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song4:1\">SNG 4:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song7:10\">SNG 7:10</a></p>\n<h2>Delight in the created order</h2>\n<h3>In God's gifts</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut26:11\">DEU 26:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:2\">ISA 55:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:12\">JER 31:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:23\">JOL 2:23</a></p>\n<h3>In one's work</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:10\">ECC 2:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut12:7\">DEU 12:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl3:22\">ECC 3:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:19\">ECC 5:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl8:15\">ECC 8:15</a></p>\n<h3>In the achievements of others</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:5\">COL 2:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod18:9\">EXO 18:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth6:9\">EST 6:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:35\">PRO 14:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:13-1Thess2:14\">1TH 2:13–2:14</a></p>\n<h2>The delight of believers in their relationship with God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:2\">PSA 9:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:1\">1SA 2:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh1:11\">NEH 1:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job22:26\">JOB 22:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:14\">PSA 9:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps13:5\">PSA 13:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:7\">PSA 31:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps35:9\">PSA 35:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:4\">PSA 37:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:16\">PSA 89:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps149:2\">PSA 149:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:46-Luke1:47\">LUK 1:46–1:47</a></p>\n<h2>Delight in wrongdoing</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps62:4\">PSA 62:4</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor13:6\">1CO 13:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps68:30\">PSA 68:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov2:12-Prov2:15\">PRO 2:12–2:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:2\">PRO 18:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:3\">ISA 66:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:18\">COL 2:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:12\">2TH 2:12</a></p>",
